entries.femaleVariant: And that guy in seven? Completely whacked. I'm tellin' ya. Gonna yank out that IV one of these days, start zeroin' people.
Don't say what? Didn't you hear what happened in Seattle? Somethin' shorted in some borg's head, smashed the entire floor. Every last soul.
I'm tellin' ya. Every gonk with an implant's a ticking time bomb.
